====== H982: בָּטַח ======

===== Source =====

a primitive root;

===== Meaning =====

properly, to  hie  for refuge (but not so  precipitately  as  H2620 ); figuratively, to  trust , be  confident  or  sure

===== Definitions =====

  - hie
  - precipitately
  - trust
  - confident
  - sure

===== Usage =====

be bold (confident, secure, sure), careless (one, woman), put confidence, (make to) hope, (put, make to) trust.
